OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776352251
OL,3,CWiltshire cow 'Beau Vine' approved for
OL,4,Cwaste carrier license
OL,6,FThere are calls for stronger
OL,7,Fbackground checks for waste carriers
OL,8,Fafter a Wiltshire cow was approved for
OL,9,Fa license.
OL,11,FTo test the government's system - the
OL,12,FCountry Land and Business Association
OL,13,Fapplied for a license for 'Beau Vine'.
OL,15,FThe CLA said all that was needed was
OL,16,Fan address, an email and to pay a
OL,17,Fsmall fee - before he was approved.
OL,19,FThe group wants more to be done to
OL,20,Fstop criminals exploiting the system
OL,21,Fto appear legitimate.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
