PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776352251
OL,3,CWiltshire cow 'Beau Vine' approved for
OL,4,Cwaste carrier license
OL,6,FAnn Maidment, Director of CLA South
OL,7,FWest and owner of Beau Vine said:
OL,8,F"Beau Vine excels at eating grass,
OL,9,Flounging in the sun and a leisurely
OL,10,Fmoo.
OL,12,F"Waste management, however, remains
OL,13,Fstubbornly beyond his remit.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776352251
OL,3,CWiltshire cow 'Beau Vine' approved for
OL,4,Cwaste carrier license
OL,6,F"That he should be approved for a
OL,7,Flicense in under three seconds reveals
OL,8,Fsomething alarming: not even the most
OL,9,Fbasic background checks are being
OL,10,Fdone. And it raises a worrying
OL,11,Fquestion: if a cow can get a license,
OL,12,Fwho is the government actually turning
OL,13,Faway?
OL,15,F"Criminals know this. They exploit
OL,16,Fthese licenses to appear legitimate,
OL,17,Fthen go on to fly-tip tonnes of waste,
OL,18,Fsome of it hazardous, endangering the
OL,19,Flivelihoods of rural communities.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776352251
OL,3,CWiltshire cow 'Beau Vine' approved for
OL,4,Cwaste carrier license
OL,6,F"A system that approves applicants
OL,7,Finstantly and without scrutiny is not
OL,8,Fregulating waste. It is smoothing the
OL,9,Fpath to dump it.
OL,11,F"Government must introduce proper
OL,12,Fchecks, verification, and standards to
OL,13,Fstop rubber-stamping fly-tippers and
OL,14,Fstart protecting the communities they
OL,15,Fharm."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for Defra said: "Waste
OL,18,Fcrime is a scourge on local
OL,19,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@FO]yD@`OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1776352251
OL,3,CWiltshire cow 'Beau Vine' approved for
OL,4,Cwaste carrier license
OL,6,F"We are working across government to
OL,7,Fwipe out illegal waste throughout the
OL,8,Fcountry and make those responsible pay
OL,9,Fincluding significant reforms to the
OL,10,Fcarriers, brokers and dealers regime.
OL,12,F"We are directly supporting the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency to stop the
OL,14,Fexploitation of our waste system,
OL,15,Fincluding a #43 million boost to waste
OL,16,Fcrime enforcement, and tougher
OL,17,Fsentences for those who break the law."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
